original: Ahnlund, Stig, förste stadsläkare, Karlskrona, f. 22/6/08 i Kristianstad av tandl. Sigfrid A. o. Signe Nilsson. G. 38 m. Britt Heijbel. Barn: Greger f. 39, Bertil 42, Kerstin 44. — Stud:-ex. i Kristianstad 26, med. kand. i Lund 30 o. med. lic. där 36. Tjg. v. psyk. klin. o. med. klin. i Lund, Jön-köp. las.. Nynäs kuranst., Are fjäll-kuranst., Jämtl. 1. centr:sanat. o. Karlskrona las., stadsläk. i Karlskrona sed. 45.
translated: Ahnlund, Stig, first city doctor, Karlskrona, b. 22/6/08 in Kristianstad to dentist Sigfrid A. and Signe Nilsson. Married in 1938 to Britt Heijbel. Children: Greger b. 1939, Bertil b. 1942, Kerstin b. 1944. - Studied high school in Kristianstad in 1926, graduated with a Bachelor of Medicine in Lund in 1930 and a medical degree in 1936. Worked at the psychiatric clinic and medical clinic in Lund, Jönköping hospital, Nynäs resort, Are mountain resort, and Jämtland Central Hospital, and served as city doctor in Karlskrona since 1945.
